lead_paragraph: Kelsey Lang scored 10 points off the bench as star forward Imani Boyette sat out with early foul trouble, and No. 6 Texas pulled away from Kansas State late to win 66-51 on Saturday night.

headline.print_headline: No. 6 Texas Women Pull Away to Beat Kansas State 66-51
